items.name: Paris, France
items.description: The City of Light offers iconic landmarks like the Eiffel Tower, world-class museums, charming cafes, and romantic Seine River cruises.
items.notes: Absolutely magical! The food was amazing and the architecture was breathtaking. A bit expensive but worth every penny.

items.name: Kyoto, Japan
items.description: Ancient capital of Japan featuring traditional temples, gardens, geisha districts, and a glimpse into Japan's rich cultural heritage.
items.notes: Beautiful temples and gardens. The fall colors were spectacular. Would recommend visiting during off-peak season to avoid crowds.

items.name: Santorini, Greece
items.description: Stunning island with white-washed buildings, blue domes, dramatic cliffs, and spectacular sunsets over the Aegean Sea.
